<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:100px; margin-top: 1.2em;"><span style="color:white"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-5346/forrestgump.jpg" style="width:100px;" alt="forrestgump.jpg" class="image" /></span>
